# Local repository paths

When the user mentions a repo by short name, resolve it to these paths. Prefer relative paths from the current workspace root.

| Name | Relative path |
|------|---------------|
| **oj-multimedia** (this app) | `.` |
| **oj-backend** | `../oj-backend` |
| **oj-workspace** (rules, docs, reports) | `..` |

If a path does not exist on disk, say so and ask whether the folder was moved or renamed.

For day-to-day editing of both projects together, open `oj-stack.code-workspace` or `oj.code-workspace` in Cursor so both folders are workspace roots.
